prompt_template:
Write a conclusion that summarizes the benefits and future outlook for laser cleaning {material} surfaces. Target audience: {target_audience} in {industry_focus}.

Requirements:
- Exactly {word_target} words
- Optimistic yet realistic tone
- Summarize key advantages of laser cleaning for {material}
- Mention emerging trends and technology developments
- Include call-to-action for readers to consider implementation
- Address ROI and long-term benefits
- Technical depth: {technical_depth}
- Natural voice target: {natural_voice_target}
- Do not include headers
- End with forward-looking statement

Content quality must meet threshold: {content_quality_threshold}
